subject: Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: Tyreke Evans capped a sterling season for the Sacramento Kings by beating out Golden State’s Stephen Curry and Milwaukee’s Brandon Jennings for the N.B.A. rookie of the year award.
